summary: Giant Sweetrolls located a little bit outside Whiterun. Don\'t eat them all right away because that\'s all that there is.
descriptionHtml:
Giant Sweetrolls located a little bit outside Whiterun, across from the stables.

Giant Sweetroll Pros: They gib you 200 instant health.

Giant Sweetroll Cons: They weight 100 lbs.

Don\'t eat them all right away because what you see on the ground is all that there is.

Perfect for shoving at Guards when they taunt you about stolen sweetrolls.
author: brokendeck
